Package de.feu.massim22.group3.map

Interface INavi

All Superinterfaces:
Disposable
All Known Subinterfaces:
INaviAgentV1, INaviAgentV2, INaviTest
All Known Implementing Classes:
Navi
public interface INavi extends Disposable
The Interface INavi defines methods for basic interaction between agents and the Navi. The Interface can be extended to define special interaction between different implementations of agents and the Navi.
Author:
Heinz Stadler, Melinda Betz (minor contribution)
